    <h1>Botswana Index Overview</h1>
    <p>Botswana requires a formal index to provide credibility, comparability, and continuity in assessing corporate performance.</p>
    <p>Unlike awards, which are often subjective and transient, indexes offer structured, data-driven benchmarks that endure over time.</p>
    <p>This aligns with national narratives such as Vision 2036, without direct government involvement, maintaining an independent stance.</p>
    <p>Index Group affirms its independence in all evaluations and operations.</p>
    <div class="accreditation">
      <p>Accredited by the Botswana Institute for Corporate Excellence (BICE)</p>
      <img src="images/bice-stamp.png" alt="BICE Accreditation Stamp">
    </div>
